title: Hitachi HNAS: Filesystems
agents: hitachi_hnas_rest
catalog: hw/storagehw/hitachi
license: GPLv2
distribution: Kuhn & Rueß GmbH
description:
 This check monitors the filesystems of a Hitachi NAS (HNAS) system
 via the File Storage REST API. It requires the special agent
 "Hitachi HNAS via REST API" to be configured for the host.

 The check reports the space usage of each filesystem and alerts
 if the configurable levels (default: 80%/90%) are exceeded. It
 also monitors the thin provisioning state and the mount status.
 By default a filesystem which is not mounted is reported as WARN,
 thin provisioning enabled but not valid as WARN, and thin
 provisioning not enabled as OK. All states are configurable via
 the rule "Hitachi HNAS Filesystems".

item:
 The label of the filesystem.

discovery:
 One service is created for each filesystem.
